query:
SELECT 
  p.id,
  p.apiId,
  p.ourPrice,
  p.quantityAvailable,
  s.name as serviceName,
  a.name as apiName
FROM prices p
JOIN services s ON p.serviceId = s.id
JOIN sms_apis a ON p.apiId = a.id
WHERE s.smshubCode = 'wa'
  AND s.active = true
ORDER BY p.apiId;
